# SDEP

Secure Device Enrollment Protocol (SDEP) — Cryptol specification

This module specifies the pure decision logic of SDEP and encodes the
22 security properties (P1–P22) from spec.md as Cryptol `property`
declarations suitable for proof with SAW/Z3.

## Types

All type definitions: [types.md](types.md)

